name: Staring back at Me
description:
A helping hand
A heartfelt smile 
The kindness you give 
Deserve another pair of eyes  

This piece is hand-drawn digitally using a stylus pen in Procreate program on an iPad Pro device – set to animation by BM.ID into mp4 file

This NFT is part of “Us” Series
Teguh Ostenrik in collaboration with BM.ID 

Some people are better at remembering places
Some people are better at remembering names
Some people are better at remembering numbers
And there are people like me
Who is better at remembering faces
That features beyond the visual

This series is particularly capturing the faces of NFT artists around the globe.
The NFT art form is relatively new compared to others. However, it can go beyond any physical border. What amazed me most was how the community of artists support each other. So this is my way to appreciate everyone in the NFT world.
